{"tid":313812,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"LIHKG環冠女神盃其他地區附額賽第一圈－Charlize Theron vs Nina Dobrev","createTime":"2017-07-08T16:07:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-09T15:33:58.000Z","uid":92376,"like":4,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3a13e924e37890273c28f82df13fbf71de1df12c","tid":313812,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T16:07:00.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">LIHKG環球女神冠軍盃其他地區附加賽名額賽第一圈</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2017-7-9 12:07am-10:07pm</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/muMD6M1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FmuMD6M1.png&h=b94fe16e&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/qJjTal0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FqJjTal0.png&h=15b689c6&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/MB9izBa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FMB9izBa.png&h=6a7cd1a3&s={SIZE}\" />Charlize Theron vs Nina Dobrev<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/KADRdM3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FKADRdM3.png&h=6f0730a8&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">賽事時限為22小時，會員可於本帖發起後22小時內於以正負評方式(前者正評;後者負評)投選心水賽事女神。<br />\n在<span style=\"color: red;\">指定時段外</span>的正負評投票<span style=\"color: red;\">將不作計算</span>在內，請會員密切留意比賽時間。</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">附加賽不設額外分數，會員請踴躍投票支持參賽者。</div>"},{"pid":"51ee123d1b832aff0d53fccdd3a60e979d2ada85","tid":313812,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T16:07:20.000Z","msg":"屌你老母開左幾次都話標題太長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal